{"questionId":"27880","questionHtml":"<p>Find, in terms of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>t</mi></math>, the coordinates of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>X</mtext></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>let <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>X</mtext></math> have coordinates <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></mfenced></math></p>\n<p><br><strong>METHOD 1</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">M</mi><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mi>x</mi></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mi>y</mi></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>2</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>3</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>6</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>5</mn><mi>t</mi></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mi>x</mi></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mi>y</mi></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced><mo>=</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">M</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>2</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>3</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>6</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>5</mn><mi>t</mi></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">M</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>14</mn></mfrac><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>1</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>4</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mo>-</mo><mn>3</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>2</mn></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"htt